Summary: several unidentified objects caught in sky portion of family outing still photos. All are similar shape size&aprox. distance; caught in multiple images(digital photos)
divs: sighting details while at baugher's farm market(orchard)in westminster maryland (carrol county) 3 october 2009 aprox.4:30 pm, my wife asked me to photograph a very large bird that she saw(a hawk flying and circling above. it was these images that we unknowingly captured some of the objects. later this day, at home and reviewing the images, we noticed that there were more objects in the sky than just the bird, tube-like or cigar shaped; depending on the perspective they could be oval or circular, but in the images they appear to be the size of a greyhound bus or larger,maybe a 1.5 to 2 miles away, 35 to 45 degrees above horizon in one photo (maybe the size of a boeing 727)they are some distance away. we found at least three in one photo, and at least one in another photo.all of the photos that we took this day were within a time-frame of an hour and a half to two hours and from differing perspectives and different zoom settings with the camera, so i'm sure that these could be of interest to someone for further study... if anyone is interested in seeing them they are welcome. as for now, i am not making any assumptions. i just want to put it out there and let others decide what they want to think about them. as for the ufo q&a's... 1.we were at the orchard picking apples and taking photos. 2.we noticed these objects after the fact while at home and reviewing the photos of the day when we noticed the anomalies in more than one photo which were taken at least 10 minutes apart and from differing degree angles and azimuths, lens settings and zooms.nikon d40x 10.2 mega pix w\ 55-200 nikor vr lens. 3. at first i thought perhaps the objects were birds, but then realized that they were something else other than birds much larger. 4.according to the photos they are all seemingly the same size, and viewed from differing altitudes and angles from our vantage points, all images include the anomalies at differing pitch and attitude from each other. 5.my feelings are unchanged reactions are intrigue and wonder. im going to get my camera checked out soon! 6. have not lost sight of it ... found it after inspecting the photographs *note: these attached images are small cropped-in portions of the originals obviously these particular modified to some point ,only to illustrate what we have seen... the originals have not been modified and are much larger then these in size and resolution and contain landmarks which may help to determine size distance and whatever else... **"1.jpg" is a cropped portion of "dsc_8566.jpg" taken a fraction of a second before "2.jpg", no anomaly. the original has not been altered. ***"2.jpg" is a cropped portion of "dsc_8567.jpg".i have increased the gamma on the hilights+.10 and zoomed in to illustrate the object better.the original has not been altered. (this was taken ~.5 hours after the bird image(dsc_8631.jpg)) ****image "3.jpg.jpg" is cropped from dsc_8631 5 items that i have seen on thios image. 3 unidentified flying objects, some trees in the bottom right corner, and a bird (that my wife asked me to take the picture of)
